OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779027072
OL,3,CNandy says EU 'world away' from what
OL,4,Cpeople want as Burnham hints at
OL,5,Crejoining
OL,7,FReopening the Brexit debate and
OL,8,Frejoining the EU is a "world away"
OL,9,Ffrom what people want, the culture
OL,10,Fsecretary has said after both Wes
OL,11,FStreeting and Andy Burnham suggested
OL,12,Fit was in the UK's best interest.
OL,14,FOn Saturday, the mayor of Manchester
OL,15,Ftold ITV News he believed there was
OL,16,F"long-term case" for rejoining the
OL,17,FEuropean Union, although he added he
OL,18,Fwas not going to advocate it in the
OL,19,Fupcoming Makerfield by-election.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779027072
OL,3,CNandy says EU 'world away' from what
OL,4,Cpeople want as Burnham hints at
OL,5,Crejoining
OL,7,FIn a speech over the weekend,
OL,8,FStreeting was even more explicit,
OL,9,Fsaying Brexit was a "catastrophic
OL,10,Fmistake," and said: "Britain's future
OL,11,Flies with Europe, and one day - one
OL,12,Fday - back in the European Union."
OL,14,FBoth Streeting and Burnham have been
OL,15,Fseen as two of the key operators
OL,16,Fangling to replace Keir Starmer as
OL,17,Fprime minister and they have begun
OL,18,Foutlining their vision for the country.
OL,20,FWatch ITV News's full interview with
OL,21,FAndy Burnham
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779027072
OL,3,CNandy says EU 'world away' from what
OL,4,Cpeople want as Burnham hints at
OL,5,Crejoining
OL,7,FBut speaking to ITV News, the
OL,8,FSecretary of State for Culture, Media
OL,9,Fand Sport Lisa Nandy said she said:
OL,10,F"I'm slightly baffled as to why
OL,11,Fanybody would think that the only
OL,12,Fanswer to the absolute kicking that
OL,13,FLabour got at the polls last Thursday
OL,14,Fis Europe."
OL,16,FShe added: "Essentially that is saying
OL,17,Fto people in towns like mine in Wigan
OL,18,Fthat we just need to go back to 2015
OL,19,Fwhen everything was fine.
OL,21,F"Everything was not fine then.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779027072
OL,3,CNandy says EU 'world away' from what
OL,4,Cpeople want as Burnham hints at
OL,5,Crejoining
OL,7,F"We've got serious action that we need
OL,8,Fto take as a country to make sure that
OL,9,Fthe economy, housing, public services
OL,10,Fwork for people in a way that they
OL,11,Fhaven't done for a really long time."
OL,13,FShe said the government was in favour
OL,14,Fof renegotiating the Brexit deal to
OL,15,F"repair some of the needless damage
OL,16,Fthat we did to people's living
OL,17,Fstandards is absolutely the right
OL,18,Fapproach.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779027072
OL,3,CNandy says EU 'world away' from what
OL,4,Cpeople want as Burnham hints at
OL,5,Crejoining
OL,7,F"I think simply going back around the
OL,8,Ftrack of having an ideological
OL,9,Fargument about whether we rejoin the
OL,10,FEuropean Union or not is a world away
OL,11,Ffrom what people are asking for."
OL,13,FNandy was also clear that if a
OL,14,Fleadership challenge was triggered,
OL,15,Fthen Starmer would stand for re-
OL,16,Felection as leader of the Labour Party
OL,17,Fand prime minister.
OL,19,FWhen asked if she supported Burnham or
OL,20,FStreeting, Nandy responded, "I'm
OL,21,Fbacking the government."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779027072
OL,3,CNandy says EU 'world away' from what
OL,4,Cpeople want as Burnham hints at
OL,5,Crejoining
OL,7,FBut Nandy also said she was
OL,8,Fcampaigning in Makerfield on Saturday
OL,9,Fand said Burnham was "extremely
OL,10,Fpopular" in the area and said Labour
OL,11,Fwould benefit from his return to
OL,12,FParliament.
OL,14,FSpeaking in his first interview since
OL,15,Fhe was cleared to run as a candidate
OL,16,Fin the Makerfield election, Burnham
OL,17,Ftold ITV News he understood the
OL,18,Fchallenge he faced.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
