CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779027072
OL,3,CNandy says EU 'world away' from what
OL,4,Cpeople want as Burnham hints at
OL,5,Crejoining
OL,7,FReform made significant gains in the
OL,8,Fregion during the recent local
OL,9,Felections, and Nigel Farage has
OL,10,Fpromised to throw everything he has at
OL,11,Fthe election.
OL,13,FThe by-election was triggered after
OL,14,Fthe current MP, Josh Simmons, resigned
OL,15,Fexplicitly so Burnham could stand.
OL,17,FBurnham is widely seen as the
OL,18,Ffavourite to replace Starmer as PM if
OL,19,Fa leadership election is triggered,
OL,20,Fdespite the fact he is not yet an MP.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
