PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779027072
OL,3,CNandy says EU 'world away' from what
OL,4,Cpeople want as Burnham hints at
OL,5,Crejoining
OL,7,FOther contenders include Streeting and
OL,8,Fformer deputy prime minister Angela
OL,9,FRayner.
OL,11,FThe prime minister has so far refused
OL,12,Fto stand down and has insisted he will
OL,13,Fcarry on in his role.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779027072
OL,3,CNandy says EU 'world away' from what
OL,4,Cpeople want as Burnham hints at
OL,5,Crejoining
OL,7,FBut since the local election, which
OL,8,Fsaw Labour lose over 1,000 seats, many
OL,9,Fin the party have viewed his authority
OL,10,Fas fatally flawed and have called for
OL,11,Fhim to outline a timetable for his
OL,12,Fresignation.
OL,14,FSpeaking to ITV News, Burnham did not
OL,15,Fdirectly say he is planning to
OL,16,Fchallenge Starmer for the top job but
OL,17,Fhe said he would take his fight "as
OL,18,Fhigh as I can go."
OL,20,FStreeting said on Saturday he would
OL,21,Frun in any leadership contest.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
